Author: zerkalisz
Title: [ANN]MetaMorph.Pro - All-in-one app to secure, manage and exchange cryptos!
Body: 7 Benefits of Decentralized Trading on Metamorph.Pro https://medium.com/@metamorphpro/7-benefits-of-decentralized-trading-on-metamorph-pro-1e39a274a1f9  There are many benefits to trading on a decentralized exchange as compared to a centralized exchange.  *Centralized exchanges (CEX’s) are custodial, which means they have custody of your coins when you make a deposit.  *Decentralized exchanges (DEX’s) are non-custodial, which means you never deposit funds onto the exchange and always retain full control of your funds. All transactions are processed on the blockchain between buyer and seller.  Here are the Top 7 benefits of using the Metamorph.Pro DEX.  1. Control Of Your Funds Stays With You 2. Security from Theft 3. Low Exchange Fees 4. Higher Liquidity 5. Privacy & Identity Protection 6. No Withdrawal Limits or Delays 7. More Currency Trade Options

Author: imyashir
Title: [ANN]MetaMorph.Pro - All-in-one app to secure, manage and exchange cryptos!
Body: There are hundreds of exchanges, however we consider ourselves not only an exchange but also more like an advanced Wallet with Portfolio, and Backup security functionality, Reports and much more while having our own METM trading pair with benefits for holders.  There are either very good exchanges, very good wallets, or very good Portfolio checking platforms, but there are very few Platforms that have all of those combined. We think we do an extremely good job at that.  Many exchanges make it extremely difficult to get started as a newbie.  We offer both the atomic swap capability which we call (Morphing) along with advanced trading functionality for those who want to do more advanced trades using Orderbook.  Take a look at ShapeShift, now add some steroids to that. Take a look at Blockfolio, now add some steroids to that. Take a look at Exodus, now add some steroids to that. Take a look at IDEX, now add some steroids to that.  See the picture?  This is MetaMorph.pro  Are you ready to Morph? Will there be purchase protection in relation to the buyer, that is, buy and receive, because if don't receive,the protection for the refund? Title: [ANN]MetaMorph.Pro - All-in-one app to secure, manage and exchange cryptos!
Body: The MetaMorph Platform Launches on the 15th of October! Development is steaming ahead and with highly dedicated and talented people working hard behind the scenes to make the platform the best it can be, we can now happily announce the launch date. Soon you will be able to use our decentralized platform to trade and exchange cryptocurrencies between the most popular ones on the market.  MetaMorph is the all-in one cryptocurrency platform to manage and securely trade your cryptocurrencies.  While we are all very busy testing and optimizing the platform and polishing things off, we would like to share a few bits of news with the community.  Incentives Those who hold more than 1,000 METM will receive discount on all trades performed in the trading section. Pair trading with METM and a premium tier for those who hold more than 10,000 METM are also in the roadmap and planning.  Competitions We are launching several competitions in the coming weeks with some of our chosen partners communities to celebrate the launch of the MetaMorph platform!  Listings We have recently listed the following cryptocurrencies on the platform and welcome them to our crypto family, connecting many communities together. BRAVE, DYLVER, CONTRACTIUM, XCRYPT, DICE, KROSS _______________________________________________________________________________ __________________________ https://medium.com/@metamorphpro/the-metamorph-platform-launches-on-the-15th-of-october-6471fcf9882d _______________________________________________________________________________ __________________________

Author: imyashir
Title: [ANN]MetaMorph.Pro - All-in-one app to secure, manage and exchange cryptos!
Body: Hey there Metamorphians!  The launch date of MetaMorph.Pro is almost here!  With only six days to go until the platform launches, the team is bursting with excitement to finally be able to share it with you all.  The platform is not only looking great, it is also very user friendly and very secure. We hope that the platform will set new standards for what users should expect from a trading platform. We will continue to drive innovation by implementing new features and functionalities to enhance the trading experience  Follow the countdown right here  We can also happily announce that MetaMorph.Pro will list the Clinicoin token at launch.  Noel Chandler from Clinicoin had the following to say:  "We’re always looking for great partners at Clinicoin and love what the MetaMorph.pro exchange brings to decentralization with its atomic swap trading. We believe decentralization has a very strong future in the cryptocurrency world and are extremely excited to be listed on MetaMorph.pro, providing our community with a next generation trading experience."  Clinicoin is a blockchain-leveraged, global healthcare platform improving health, wellness, and medical research, rewarding community users for taking part in health and research-oriented activities. Focused on improving engagement and adherence, the Clinicoin project's mission is to advance global health and wellness by encouraging health innovations through an open-source, universal digital health platform.

Author: imyashir
Title: [ANN]MetaMorph.Pro - All-in-one app to secure, manage and exchange cryptos!
Body: The full updated version of MetaMorph.pro will be available to the public during Q3 2018.  Here are the benefits of MetaMorph.pro moving forward:  ➡️ Simply exchange a coin within 60 seconds flat on average or do advanced trading with full Orderbook functionality. ➡️ No KYC needed in order to exchange coins or trade, totally anonymous. ➡️ 100% safe and secure including wallet backup functionality. ➡️ Check portfolio and easily view what your best investments are. ➡️ Discounts and benefits when holding METM coin within the MetaMorph.pro wallet. ➡️ Easily replace long wallet addresses as usernames in a address book for easier sending and receiving. ➡️ Full reports feature to keep organized on history of trades per specific dates, great for bookkeeping. ➡️ Simply sync your token portfolio using Ledger, MetMask, Parity, Mist. ➡️ Get trading alerts and notifications to suggest when is the right time to buy or sell. ➡️ Use the slick web interface or download the app on desktop or mobile devices.  More information here: https://metamorph.pro/

Body: Hi friends!  MetaMorph is now listed on Bitgur price index - https://bitgur.com/coin/METM! You can add it to customizable watchlist and create advanced price alerts.  Coin Tracking There is Coin Tracking Alert in Bitgur Alerts. Add it once and you will receive important information about MetaMorph.
